title: St. Jude's Ranch for Children - Jingle Bell Run
text:
St. Jude's Ranch for Children - Jingle Bell Run Where 
8:00 a.m. Saturday, Dec. 12, 2015 Categories 
Events, Fundraisers, Sports The family friendly event will be held in and around historic Gruene Hall in Gruene, TX (New Braunfels, TX) on December 12, 2015. The chip-timed 5K will begin at 8:00AM with the kidsâ€™ 1K to follow. There will be opportunities for photos with Santa, hot coffee and hot chocolate to keep you warm and Christmas shopping in Gruene after the race!
